<br>
Some other items that were of interest to me were the points he made that Croud Control will be completely different, the cost of dying has changed a little, and the item decay was removed.  Now it's part of the cost of dying - if you die your weapons decay a little bit.  Oh and the Artisan class sounds like it's actually going to be a BLAST to play <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Personally - I will be playing EQ II and I am positive that I will have 2 characters - and one of them is definately going to be an Artisan.  No more &quot;Stack - Combine - Repeat&quot;!!!<br>
<br>
WooHaA!<br>
~Kire~<br>
